A user is someone who uses, modifies or copies rexlib in any way
A license is a contract that the user must agree to, if they use rexlib


Rexlib is completely free
A user is allowed to modify, and resell modified versions of rexlib, however they can not sell the original copy of rexlib without adding any additions.
To sell the new version the modifications must be significant and/or integrated into a larger project
An user can sell a project that uses rexlib in any way

